## 7. Burp Practical Workflow
1. 403/401 milne pe Repeater mein request bhejo
2. Ek-ek header add karke response code check karo
3. Combination try karo (`X-Forwarded-For` + `X-Original-URL` saath mein)
4. HTTP method change karke retry karo (Verb Tampering)
5. URL manipulation tricks (trailing slash, case change, encoding) try karo
6. Agar JWT-based auth hai, token decode karke role tampering try karo
7. Turbo Intruder se race condition bhi test karo agar action + check alag endpoints pe ho

